---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="工具集 · LoveAlwaysHere" description="实用在线工具集合">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-violet-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">&#x1f527; 工具集</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">日常开发和生活所需的在线小工具</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/tools/password" class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-cyan-500/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-600/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">&#x1f510;</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100">门锁密码生成器</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">施工队智能门锁密码分配</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">为施工队分配楼栋楼层的智能门锁密码，支持 6-8 位数字，自动记录分配历史。</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-cyan-400 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          <span>立即使用</span>
          <span>&#8594;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800/50 bg-gray-900/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">&#x1f6e0;</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-600">更多工具</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-700 mt-0.5">即将上线</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">更多实用工具正在开发中，敬请期待...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>